S . AFRICA ' S MATHOMO CAUTIONS FURTHER . South African black empowerment Mathomo Group Ltd retailer said on Monday that the company was still involved in talks which could affect its share price . The company gave no further details but urged shareholders to exercise caution in share dealings until further notice . Mathomo said on April 13 it had bought the entire issued share capital of Tonclin Investment Holdings ( Pty ) Ltd for 24 . 6 million rand . Tonclin holds Eldons Group , a retailer and wholesaler of educational , commercial and general stationery . - - Johannesburg newsroom + 2711 482 - 1003 
